thread.title_full: Express Medical Supply reviewed by Karen Gallagher

author: Karen Gallagher
title: Karen Gallagher
text:
Finding the product I needed went quickly and efficiently online. Check out too.
My only request: could there be a lower shipping rate for such lightweight packages such as mine? For example, might I be able to pay no more than the cost of the item if it is of very little weight?
Thank you for mailing it so speedily.
